{"tid":1930364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【TVB廣告商，醜聞日日數】馬路炸彈 = Lexus凌志 (17 Mar)","createTime":"2020-03-17T13:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T02:22:23.000Z","uid":267969,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"56cbedf9f99c2651a401adba4f740c997e77ea58","tid":1930364,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請各位marketing銘記以下格言</span><br />\nTVB廣告商，醜聞被人唱</span></strong><br />\n團隊好辛苦搵醜聞資料，記得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【永久抵制精選@17 Mar 2020】</span></strong></span><br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.永久抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5. 互like留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 留言貼醜聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (新)</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Lexus 凌志</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/LexusHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLexusHK%2F&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=82b1f95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/LexusHK/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※留言template</strong></span></span><br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，誤導市民。貴公司違反向市民承諾，在無綫電視投放廣告，本人將轉用其他品牌，並永久抵制貴公司，敬請注意。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net